snippet.title: (Unreleased Game) EA Create: Snap - Nintendo DS, 2009 [Full Gameplay, Lost Media]
snippet.description:
Here it is. The unreleased game by Barking Lizards Technologies, EA Create: Snap for the Nintendo DS.

If you would like to hear more information on this game, check out Hard4Games' video here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q-gTJx9c2lI

Thank you to Hard4Games and Codebound for their help! Without them, this wouldn't have been possible. 

EA Create Snap Download: https://archive.org/details/ea-create-snap-nintendo-ds-unreleased-early-prototype

Please go support them!
Hard4Games: https://x.com/hard4games
CodeBound: https://x.com/_codebound_

EA Create: Snap was developed on the Nitro Development Kit, but it's a game for the Nintendo DSi? Yeah, it's a little odd...
